    "title": "Episode 4",
    "overview": "The rules of the imperial kitchen: The little cook accidentally broke the rules in the kitchen while cooking. Xiao Lizi gave special training to the little cook and barely passed, and Xiao Lizi suggested to give Cixi some meat.",
