  {
    "number": 5,
    "title": "Episode 5",
    "overview": "Where is the meat? : Little Cook and Little Lizi searched for meat everywhere, but only found three eggs, but one egg was stolen by a mouse. When they were chasing the mouse, one egg was broken, and the other hatched a chick and ran away. In a fit of anger, the two caught mice to vent their anger. Offering a dish made of rat meat, Lafayette just took a bite and shouted: \"Xiao Li Zi—!\"",
    "air_date": "2007-08-29",
